casebody.data:
Jacqueline DUNN
v.
Honorable Nancy NORELLI, District Court Judge. No. 97P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 2, 2006. Jacqueline Dunn, Pro Se. Nancy Norelli, Pro Se.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 24th day of February 2006 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Mecklenburg County:

"Denied by order of the Court in Conference this the 2nd day of March 2006."
